            <title><![CDATA[习近平率领政治局常委赴陕西延安]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/36942d4861094cab9ae2ed4ff54a433d.jpg?itok=EW4nPb9k" title="习近平（左四）带领中共中央政治局常委赴陕西延安瞻仰延安革命纪念地。（新华社微博）" alt="习近平（左四）带领中共中央政治局常委赴陕西延安瞻仰延安革命纪念地。（新华社微博）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/36942d4861094cab9ae2ed4ff54a433d.jpg?itok=EW4nPb9k" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
